{"tid":1843902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得澳門個新特首賀仔好撚陰濕","createTime":"2020-01-26T11:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:45:33.000Z","uid":20241,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"85ea7a8dbb09cd71180a4016172909a44faacd03","tid":1843902,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"早幾日話免費醫肺炎<br />\n轉頭又話縮短通關又話要兩邊探熱今日又要醫生紙<br />\n聽日又唔知玩咩花招<br />\n擺明撚鳩班支那人<br />\n焗班友黎曬香港醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55dbe72090ac628850a06e5bed88da4e16269e8","tid":1843902,"uid":198590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">一日到黑就淨係錢, 樓價股價, 69已經話緊人收錢出黎行</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#20241 - 高息股</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>我有一計可破黃色經濟圈 在此獻上希望可以俾個AO小妹做下 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>最近班黑衣暴徒越來越倡狂<br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n只要分出邊啲係黃店<br />\n再安排防暴長駐 入店既年青人全部都要查證+事後拘捕(擾亂社會秩序+非法集結)<br />\n咁樣黃色經濟圈好快就會不攻自破<br />\n香港好快可以回復正常<br />\n希望特首接納</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1802010/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1802010/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>冇事啦香港人贏左啦港女升返曬啦大家快啲返工返學啦 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>各位手足付出左咁多<br />\n贏得咁辛苦<br />\n大家俾啲掌聲自己好唔好<br />\n好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Flomoji%2F12.png&h=b2e0eb94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Flm2%2Fsupport.gif&h=4d4183e9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1758161/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1758161/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>水炮車其實都幾大部 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>支持警察係大街射死你地班暴徒<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1664677/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1664677/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>核彈都唔割！嗱不過搞裝修 紅綠燈 叫太多神獸就割架啦 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>始終人種同基因係咁就係咁<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1628233/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1628233/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港太亂 希望政府強力執法 全港斷網 斷電話3日搜捕暴徒 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>周圍破壞 又上網亂咁抹黑警方同政府<br />\n我地一般市民真係忍唔到啦！<br />\n應立即斷網斷電話 實施戒嚴三日 